season_counts = him_df.groupby("season")["expid"].count().reset_index()

#    
season_labels = season_counts["season"]
expeditions_values = season_counts["expid"]

#       
him_df["bcdate"] = pd.to_datetime(him_df["bcdate"])
him_df["month"] = him_df["bcdate"].dt.month
him_df["year"] = him_df["bcdate"].dt.year

#     
expeditions_by_month = him_df.groupby("month")["expid"].count().reset_index()

#      
fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(16, 6))

#    -     
wedges, texts, autotexts = axes[0].pie(expeditions_values, labels=season_labels, autopct="%1.1f%%", 
                                       colors=plt.cm.coolwarm(np.linspace(0, 1, len(season_labels))),
                                       textprops={'fontsize': 12})

#      
for i, text in enumerate(texts):
    axes[0].text(1.2, 0.8 - (i * 0.1), f"{season_labels[i]}: {expeditions_values[i]}", 
                 fontsize=12, color="black", bbox=dict(facecolor="white", edgecolor="black", boxstyle="round,pad=0.5"))

axes[0].set_title("     ", fontsize=14)

#    -    
sns.lineplot(data=expeditions_by_month, x="month", y="expid", marker="o", color="b", ax=axes[1])
axes[1].set_xlabel("")
axes[1].set_ylabel(" ")
axes[1].set_title("     ")
axes[1].grid(True)

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
